# Projet DHT PeerSim

This project implements a Chord-like Distributed Hash Table (DHT) on a ring topology, simulated using the [PeerSim](http://peersim.sourceforge.net/) high-level P2P network simulator (v1.0.5) in event-driven mode.

## Project Structure

This archive is composed of:
- `src/`: Contains the application source code (`dht/` package) and the modified simulator source (`peersim/` package).
- `dht_config.cfg`: The main configuration file defining the simulation parameters and events.
- `peersim-1.0.5.jar`: Java archive containing the compiled PeerSim bytecode.
- `jep-2.3.0.jar` & `djep-1.0.0.jar`: Java Mathematical Expression Parser libraries needed by the PeerSim core (distributed under GPL).

## Prerequisites

- [cite_start]**Java Development Kit (JDK):** Version 17 or higher is required[cite: 771].
- **Environment:** Windows PowerShell or Linux/Mac Bash. 
[cite_start]*(Note: The commands below use `;` as the classpath separator for Windows. If you are on Linux/Mac, replace the `;` with `:`)*[cite: 820].

## Compilation

[cite_start]To compile the project, navigate to the root directory of the extracted archive and run the following command to compile all source files[cite: 783]:

```powershell
javac -classpath "src;peersim-1.0.5.jar;jep-2.3.0.jar;djep-1.0.0.jar" src/dht/*.java src/peersim/*.java src/peersim/config/*.java src/peersim/core/*.java src/peersim/dynamics/*.java src/peersim/edsim/*.java src/peersim/graph/*.java src/peersim/rangesim/*.java src/peersim/reports/*.java src/peersim/transport/*.java src/peersim/util/*.java src/peersim/vector/*.java

📁 Projet_DHT_PeerSim/
├── 📄 Makefile
├── 📄 dht_config.cfg
├── 📁 lib/
│ └── 📄 peersim-1.0.5.jar
└── 📁 src/dht/
    ├── 📄 DHTMessage.java
    ├── 📄 DHTProtocol.java
    ├── 📄 DHTInitializer.java
    ├── 📄 JoinLeaveControl.java
    ├── 📄 MessageSenderControl.java
    └── 📄 StorageTestControl.java
